e, history, and biology.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 7aPOETRY / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of Chicago Complete eBook-Package 2024z978311079731240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780226831541423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780226831541/original  a978-3-11-079731-2  University of Chicago Complete eBook-Package 2024b2024  aGBV-deGruyter-alles